				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Di%C3%AAm-s%C6%A1n/poem-2sT3sW2BVRnHt7lVFCAMGw">Bạch Diêm sơn - 白鹽山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/B%E1%BB%99-v%E1%BA%ADn-B%E1%BA%A1ch-Mai-Phan-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Ho%C3%A0n-Th%E1%BB%8B-bi%E1%BB%83u-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-ho%E1%BA%A1-chi/poem-5p8172hFUEi2_O97y1NK6w">Bộ vận Bạch Mai Phan Ngọc Hoàn “Thị biểu đệ” hoạ chi - 步韻白梅潘玉環示表弟和之</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/Khai-Nghi%C3%AAm-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-Ug6pP1nw6eIAs6JFO-TjWg">Khai Nghiêm tự bi ký - 開嚴寺碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-K%E1%BB%B3-kh%C3%AD/poem-CG2qhJF0z8Lnj6wrDzFSmQ">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Kỳ khí” - 奉和御製奇氣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/author-7XXX3GnZ0T6el9FCsBAeug">Ngô Hoán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-th%E1%BB%ABa-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-LHzRT_2tYsZxedOAYTvWlg">Phụng tặng Vi tả thừa trượng nhị thập nhị vận - 奉贈韋左丞丈二十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/Thi%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%B4-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91-ca/poem-AIgicgej92YFc1rwp6U4Cg">Thiên Đô bộc bố ca - 天都瀑布歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/author-KdxnA4RirR7LsAi6oOaAoA">Tiền Khiêm Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/T%E1%BB%AB-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-minh-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-CmcW-aGSq0U6WnbHUzXRPg">Từ Ân tự bi minh tịnh tự - 慈恩寺碑銘并序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4-S%E1%BB%9F-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%C3%AAm-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-VusrYuqrkvq24lkjJ2HUYQ">Tương thích Ngô Sở, lưu biệt Chương sứ quân lưu hậu kiêm mạc phủ chư công, đắc liễu tự - 將適吳楚，留別章使君留後兼幕府諸公，得柳字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/V%C3%A3n-t%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-c%C3%B4ng/poem-cDElVqf2JwRbA8T7Kf-a_A">Vãn tư đồ công - 輓司徒公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
